'''赞比亚国民议会'''（{{lang-en|National Assembly of Zambia}}）是[[赞比亚|赞比亚]]的[[国家|国家]][[立法机关|立法机关]]。赞比亚国民议会实行[[一院制|一院制]]，由167名[[议员|议员]]（包括156名直選議員、8名委任議員、副總統、[[议长|议长]]和第一副議長）组成。<ref name=ipu01>{{cite web |url=http://archive.ipu.org/parline-e/reports/2359_E.htm |title=IPU PARLINE database: ZAMBIA (National Assembly), Last elections |accessdate=2021-10-05}}</ref>每届议会任期5年。现任议长是{{le|内莉·穆蒂|Nelly Mutti}}，於2021年9月3日接替前任議長帕特里克·馬蒂比尼上任。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.lusakatimes.com/2021/09/03/prominent-lusaka-lawyer-nelly-mutti-elected-as-the-first-ever-woman-speaker-of-the-national-assembly/ |title=Prominent Lusaka Lawyer Nelly Mutti elected as the first ever woman Speaker of the National Assembly |date=2021-09-03 |website=lusakatimes.com}}</ref>

